text = "AH - After Hali
-26AH - Hali born
0AH - Hali comes to power
38AH - Hali retires
63AH - Hali dies
322AH - Scareye banishment
343AH - Present day

SR - Stoneland Reign
0SR - Stoneland Empire forms, they take over Jiralta and Shreev (used to border Jiralta)
677SR - Current day

BF - Befre Form
0BF - Two nations and the kings join up to form Befre
1237BF - Current day

PD - Post First Man's Departure
0PD - First Man leaves
2996PD - Current day

PD Calendar - Each month lasts 30 days, at the end there's 5 days of celebration known as the Feastdays
Feastdays are celebrated by those who follow the PD calendar and most of Volin, due to Zengef's influence, but they do also spread to outside nations that don't even follow the calendar

Elvusian - 12th month
Feastdays - 5 days
Day 1 - 
Day 2 -
Day 3 -
Day 4 - Smolderings - Each person burns an item important to them, happen at night under the sky
Day 5 -"
